      "slideNumber": 6,
      "title": "Merge sort",
      "content": [
        "Merge Sort continuously cuts the array in half until it cannot be divided further (arrays of 1 element).",
        "Then, it repeatedly merges the sub-lists to produce new sorted sub-lists until there is only one sorted list remaining."
      ],
      "ocrContent": "",
      "notes": "",
      "images": [],
      "isTextLight": false,
      "isScreenshot": false
    },
